data.description: Acreage alert! This 4 bedroom/ 2 bath home is conveniently located approximately a half mile from hard surface. There is updated electrical and renovated kitchen in bathrooms. There is new floor in the front sunroom. This home sits on approximately 4 acres and has a nice tree line for wind break on the north. Can you take a look and make it yours just in time for the holidays.
